data.title: Macalester alumnus Kofi Annan returns for Institute renaming in his honor
data.meta_description: Very happy to see this acknowledgement of a great international leader. Kofi Annan, the seventh Secretary-General of the United Nations, winner of the 2001 Nobel Peace Prize, and member of the Macalester class of 1961, will be visiting campus Monday, May 7, 2018.
